&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Support business development activities, including partnership evaluations, acquisition opportunities, and strategic transactions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Conduct financial, operational, and commercial due diligence on potential opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with finance, operations, engineering, commercial, and executive leadership teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Assist in developing business cases and investment recommendations for senior management.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Prepare clear, concise, and accurate technical and business communications for internal and external stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Manage multiple workstreams simultaneously while maintaining exceptional attention to detail.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
