&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;How You Will Make an Impact:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;District Manager&lt;/strong&gt; is responsible for supervising and training field personnel while ensuring maintenance of field shops, inventory, production, and fabrication in their designated region. The Operations Chief provides professional service and support for customers by ensuring field service installation, startup, repairs, and maintenance for Atlas generators.&amp;nbsp; Must be willing to work in all outdoor climates, be on call, and travel to various Atlas customers within their designated region.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Supervises all field facility activities including but not limited to procurement, maintenance, and quality control to ensure optimum production.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Responsible for the scheduling and coordination of field activities, including but not limited to, employee compliance, training, vacations, shift scheduling, and other items as needed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Reviews and analyzes reports for production, fabrication, quality control, maintenance, and operations to troubleshoot any necessary product issues.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Helps to develop and implement operating methods and procedures designed to eliminate operating problems and improve product quality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
